I tried @mcaffeineofficial Super Glow Flash Facial Mask, and it truly lives up to its name✨

It instantly brightens my skin, thanks to the combination of AHA, BHA, and PHA, which gently exfoliate and remove dryness. What I love most is that it doesn’t irritate my skin—the aloe extract 🍃 provides a soothing, calming effect, making it perfect even for sensitive skin.

#flashfacial #glowyskin

Just a little makeup touch for my beach day🌞

I only used two products:
First up — @theearthrhythm Glow Surge sunscreen
It’s a no brainer for a beach day, and since it’s a spray bottle, reapplying is a breeze.
Second — @kirobeauty lip and cheek tint in shade Beach Peach. Just three dots on my cheeks and lips for that naturally flushed look🌸
